  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Use of amniotic membrane(AMT) and platelet rich plasma (PRP) clot for closure of central&#xD;
      corneal perforation&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Use of amniotic membrane and platelet rich plasma clot for closure of central corneal&#xD;
      perforation either post infective or posttraumatic&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
